                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d782">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Eddy</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-12-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 20, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Eddy reports that he has requested the foreign office to instruct Russian
                    consuls to give every assistance in telegraphing powers of attorney. All powers
                    of attorney should be telegraphed immediately. It is practically impossible to
                    get anything done in the different ministries during the Christmas holidays up
                    to January 7.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
